                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Loomis</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Russell.</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-05-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Loomis informs Mr. Russell that Mr. Frank Plumley has been appointed umpire
                    for the British and Dutch commissions, and instructs him to convey this
                    information to the Venezuelan Govern-</p>
